## API Connector Matrix

| Domain       | Service                     | Auth       | Typical Scopes / Notes |
|--------------|-----------------------------|------------|-------------------------|
| Video/Social | YouTube Data API            | OAuth      | upload/read; requires youtube + youtube.upload scopes |
|              | YouTube metrics (readonly)  | API Key    | channel/video metrics; cache to reduce quota |
|              | TikTok Content Posting      | OAuth      | upload init + transfer; user finishes in TikTok inbox |
|              | Instagram Graph             | OAuth      | instagram_basic, pages_show_list; Creator/Business only |
|              | LinkedIn UGC                | OAuth      | w_member_social, OpenID basics; POST v2/ugcPosts |
|              | Pinterest                   | OAuth      | standard OAuth, token exchange/refresh |
| Design       | Canva Apps SDK              | API Key    | embed + sync design workflows |
|              | Figma REST                  | Token/OAuth| PAT or OAuth2; design syncing |
| Storage      | Supabase                    | Service key| auth + storage; protect via RLS |
|              | AWS S3                      | Access keys| bucket storage, multipart upload |
| Analytics    | GA4 Measurement Protocol    | API Secret | server-side conversions, events |
| Email/CRM    | Resend/SendGrid/Mailchimp/ConvertKit/HubSpot | API Keys | transactional + marketing sends |
| Ecommerce    | Stripe                      | Secret Key | payments, webhooks |
|              | Shopify                     | Admin Token| listings, orders, media |
|              | Etsy / Printify             | API Keys   | listings, mockups, fulfillment |
| Community    | Discord / Slack             | Bot Token  | webhooks, slash-commands |
| AI/Media     | OpenAI / Anthropic / Google GenAI / Replicate / Stability / ElevenLabs / AssemblyAI | API Keys | Gen-AI, TTS, STT, image/video |

---

## Architecture (Bolt.new)

- **/src/connectors/** â†’ tiny wrappers w/ env validation (Zod)  
- **/src/workflows/** â†’ job queue handlers (upload â†’ post â†’ schedule â†’ fetch metrics)  
- **/src/rbac/** â†’ roles, scopes, policy checks  
- **/api/** â†’ OAuth callbacks + webhook receivers (Stripe, etc.)  
- **/scripts/** â†’ health checks, smoke tests for connectors  

---

## Security Practices
- **RBAC**: clearly separate viewer, editor, and admin roles.  
- **Secrets**: all API keys/tokens managed in Bolt.new environment UI.  
- **Scopes**: grant only the minimal scopes (least privilege).  
- **Data**: enforce Supabase Row Level Security + signed S3 URLs.  

